 Babymetal与Poppy共享“激烈”合作新单曲，'从我到U' https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymetal-share-intense-collaborative-new-new-single-with-poppy-from-me-me-me-to-u-3851855?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = babymetal-share-intense-collaborative new-single-with-with-with-poppy-from-me-me-to-uTom Skinner Fri, 04 Apr 2025 08:04:11 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetal https://www.nme.com/?p=3851855 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/BABYMETALFromMeToU-Poppy-collaborative-single-news.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="婴儿金属和罂粟出版社照片" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/BABYMETALFromMeToU-Poppy-collaborative-single-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/BABYMETALFromMeToU-Poppy-collaborative-single-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/BABYMETALFromMeToU-Poppy-collaborative-single-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/BABYMETALFromMeToU-Poppy-collaborative-single-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/BABYMETALFromMeToU-Poppy-collaborative-single-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/BABYMETALFromMeToU-Poppy-collaborative-single-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>后铁杆曲目将出现在该乐队即将发行的专辑“ Metal Forth”上</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymetal-share-intense-collaborative-new-single-with-poppy-from-me-to-u-3851855">Babymetal分享与Poppy的“激烈”合作新单曲，从我到U&#39;</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/BABYMETALFromMeToU-Poppy-collaborative-single-news.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="婴儿金属和罂粟出版社照片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/BABYMETALFromMeToU-Poppy-collaborative-single-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/BABYMETALFromMeToU-Poppy-collaborative-single-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/BABYMETALFromMeToU-Poppy-collaborative-single-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/BABYMETALFromMeToU-Poppy-collaborative-single-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/BABYMETALFromMeToU-Poppy-collaborative-single-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/BABYMETALFromMeToU-Poppy-collaborative-single-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/babymetal">Babymetal</a>发行了一部合作的新单曲，其中包含<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/poppy">罂粟花</a>- 在下面听“从我到你”。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="1070" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymetal-download-2024-interview-bring-me-the-horizon-3767431"><b>婴儿金属说他们“根本没有改变”，因为他们的成功</b></a></li></ul><p>这首歌将出现在日本Kawaii Metal Band的第五张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymetal-announce-new-album-metal-forth-with-poppy-spiritbox-and-more-3850725">“ Metal Forth”</a>上，该专辑将于6月13日通过Capitol Records（<a href="https://link.fans/babymetal" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处预订/预播</a>）到达。</p><p>在谈到他们雷鸣般的铁杆后新曲目时，该小组将“从我到你”描述为“ kawaii金属歌曲（那个）是从婴儿金属和罂粟之间的合作中诞生的”。</p><p>他们补充说：“在新东京环境中查看Poppy的喊叫声和Babymetal的舞蹈！Kawaii在整个强烈的声音中都洒满了！Kimi ni Todoke！”</p><p> Poppy解释说：“多年来，我一直是Babymetal的粉丝，我很高兴这首歌终于来这里了！他们如此启发了我，享受“从我到你到你”！” </p><p><iframe title="婴儿金属 - 从我到你的壮举。罂粟（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qayP_YUrf9I?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>该单曲伴随着由Poppy主演的高概念官方视频。它还认为，婴儿金属在“破坏边缘的未来派世界摇摇欲坠”中释放了他们的标志性编舞。</p><p>在视觉效果的尽头，Poppy爆炸性地转变为一条龙 - 在灾难中舞蹈中的婴儿舞在周围的火和大屠杀中出现。在上面调整。</p><p> “金属”还将包含与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spiritbox">Spiritbox</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-morello">Tom Morello</a> ，Bloodywood， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/polyphia">Polyphia</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slaughter-to-prevail">Slaughter</a>之类的团队合作。即将发行的专辑紧随2023年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymetal-end-hiatus-with-announcement-of-new-album-the-other-one-3326522">“另一个”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymetal-announce-2025-uk-and-european-tour-with-poppy-and-bambie-thug-3805391">Babymetal计划于5月启动英国和欧洲巡回演出</a>，在布鲁塞尔森林国家竞技场（Brussels&#39;s Forest National Arena）开始。这次跋涉将在5月30日在伦敦O2举行的大型演出结束。罂粟将加入他们的巡回演出，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Bambie-Thug">班比·提格（Bambie Thug）</a>也将参加巡回演出。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fbabymetal-tickets%2Fartist%2F1993807" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>（英国）和<a href="http://www.babymetal.com/tour" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>（欧洲）找到剩余的门票。</p><p>然后，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-veil-brides">黑面纱新娘</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jinjer">Jinjer</a>和Bloodywood的支持下<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymetal-share-details-of-2025-north-american-tour-with-support-from-black-veil-brides-and-more-3847250">，乐队开始参加北美巡回演出</a>。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/babymetal-tickets/artist/1993807?irgwc=1&amp;clickid=1K9zKT0QHxycWlX3oQViwW06Uks1-MSJm2V1Ug0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;impradid=2862475&amp;REFERRAL_ID=tmfeedbuyat2862475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_2862475&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;impradname=NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;ircid=4272" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里找到剩余的门票</a>。 </p><p><iframe title="Babymetal在2019年Glastonbury：在Billie Eilish上，与我一起工作地平线和“金属银河”" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qE0goaxIzOg?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>去年夏天， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/download-festival-2024-busted-wheatus-tom-morello-enter-shikari-among-22-new-names-on-line-up-3578747#:~:text=The%2022%20acts%20will%20join,Soup%2C%20Heilung%2C%20Polyphia%2C%20Thy">Babymetal在2024年下载节上玩了一个主舞台</a>。该组织<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymetal-download-2024-interview-bring-me-the-horizon-3767431">在后台接受<i>NME</i>讲话时</a>说，他们不想在即将举行的演出中偏离他们的根源。</p><p> “你知道什么吗？我们一点都没有改变，” Su-Metal解释说，在首张录音室专辑10年后，回顾了乐队的演变。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymetal-announce-new-album-metal-forth-with-poppy-spiritbox-and-more-3850725"><p> “我们一直是婴儿金属，我们的样子，我们还有很长的路要走。[现在在这里]感谢所有支持我们的人，无论是我们的粉丝，媒体，员工，甚至是我们以前见过的其他乐队。”</p><p>在2024年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-knocked-loose-and-poppy-crushing-new-single-suffocate-3749930">Poppy与敲门曲折的曲目“ Soverocate”合作</a>。这首歌<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-see-the-full-list-of-winners-3833854#:~:text=Beyonc%C3%A9%20and%20Miley%20Cyrus%20have,for%20'Now%20And%20Then'.">在Grammys 2025被提名为最佳金属表演</a>，但最终输给了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gojira">Gojira&#39;s&#39;Mea</a> Culpa（啊！）ira！）。</p><h3> <strong>Babymetal的“金属”的曲目列表是：</st